.br
\fIsegmentsize\fP max capacity of sending\&. 
.RE
.PP
\fBReturns:\fP
.RS 4
Bytes sended on success\&. ERROR on failure (which is defined in \fBG-2301-03-P1-types\&.h\fP), and it writes the description of the error in the log file\&. 
.RE
